	<Title>
		Sleep and weight gain: What&apos;s the connection?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Sleep duration may be a risk factor for weight gain.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is too little sleep a cause of weight gain?
	</Question>
